<module>
    <h>obair</h>
    <p><g>obair</g>
        <en>work</en> is a feminine <a href="?xx=nouns/simple_common_nouns">simple common
        noun</a>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>obair</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>obair</m> – nominative/dative singular</li>
                <li><m>obrach</m> – genitive singular</li>
                <li><m>obraichean</m> – plural</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <section id="definiteness">
            <h>definiteness</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>indefinite <ul>
                            <li>singular <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>obair</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>obair</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – taobh <m>obrach</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>plural <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>obraichean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>obraichean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – taobh <m>obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>definite <ul>
                            <li>singular <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>an obair</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>an obair</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – taobh <m>na h-obrach</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>plural <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>na h-obraichean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>na h-obraichean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – taobh <m>nan obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
        <section id="number">
            <h>number</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>singular <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>obair</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>obair</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – taobh <m>obrach</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>an obair</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>an obair</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – taobh <m>na h-obrach</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>plural <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>obraichean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – ann an <m>obraichean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – taobh <m>obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>na h-obraichean</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – anns <m>na h-obraichean</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – taobh <m>nan obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
        <section id="case">
            <h>case</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>nominative <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – <m>obair</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – <m>obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – <m>an obair</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – <m>na h-obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>dative <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – ann an <m>obair</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – ann an <m>obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – anns <m>an obair</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – anns <m>na h-obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>genitive <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – taobh <m>obrach</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – taobh <m>obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – taobh <m>na h-obrach</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – taobh <m>nan obraichean</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
        <section id="forms-notes">
            <h>notes</h>
            <p>Note the following – <ul>
                    <li>An alternative form of the genitive singular is <g>oibre</g>.</li>
                    <li>An alternative form of the plural is <g>oibrichean</g>.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>dependents</h>
        <section id="deps-bare">
            <h>bare</h>
            <p>Like other nouns, <g>obair</g> can occur on its own without any dependents – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri ag <m>obair</m> agus tha Calum ag <m>obair</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is working and Malcolm is working.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
