        <section id="deps-mods">
            <h>modifiers</h>
            <p><g>obair</g> can occur with the usual verb modifiers.</p>
            <p>Examples with locative modifiers – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri agus Calum ag obair <m>anns an achadh</m> an diugh.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary and Malcolm are working in the field today.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6–7</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with manner modifiers –<xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Calum sgìth: tha e ag obair <m>gu trang</m> anns an achadh.</gd>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>

